{
  "chapter": 70,
  "chapter_summary": "盐船进入长江后遭遇大江会伏击，寇仲与徐子陵率众抗击。大江会副帮主裴炎与王薄之子王魁介联手追击，双方在江上展开激战。寇仲与徐子陵利用烟幕掩护，与王魁介交手，最终将其逼退。战后盐船避入支流休整，寇仲将宝刀命名为\"井中月\"，徐子陵则为段玉成等四人设计内功心法。两人讨论后续行程，决定夜闯江都李子通防线，继续运送私盐至关中。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "咯！咯！咯！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 5,
      "line_end": 5
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "进来吧！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 7,
      "line_end": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我有很不祥的预感，今晚定会有麻烦的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 13,
      "line_end": 13
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "斗力只是下下之策，你有甚么鬼主意呢？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 19,
      "line_end": 19
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你不是想凿沉人家的船吧？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 45,
      "line_end": 45
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "龙君",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 81,
      "line_end": 81
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "弃船！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 93,
      "line_end": 93
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_gui",
      "speaker_name": "麻贵",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "可以随时放烟幕了！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 127,
      "line_end": 127
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_gui",
      "speaker_name": "麻贵",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "看我手势！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 129,
      "line_end": 129
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "阁下何人！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 147,
      "line_end": 147
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "来得好！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 179,
      "line_end": 179
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "叮",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 181,
      "line_end": 181
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "嗤！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 203,
      "line_end": 203
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他的轻功也很不错。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 217,
      "line_end": 217
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "最多是五五之数。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 223,
      "line_end": 223
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我要为我的宝刀正名。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 239,
      "line_end": 239
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "井中月！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 253,
      "line_end": 253
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你将就点吧！一世人两兄弟，哪计较得这么多呢？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 259,
      "line_end": 259
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "今晚我们是否要硬闯江都李子通那一关呢？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 303,
      "line_end": 303
    }
  ],
